    <title>Strategic Capacity Commitment: A Channel Competition Perspective</title>
    <updated>2026-01-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Shuguang Zhang, Wei Shi Lim, Lucy Gongtao Chen</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;b&gt;Marketing Science&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;This paper examines how capacity commitment shapes strategic interactions between asymmetric channels—one centralized and one decentralized—and reveals that a centralized manufacturer’s capacity commitment can mitigate price competition and benefit both channels.</content>
